  1→/**
  2→ * Objective & Behavior Acceptance Test Kit
  3→ *
  4→ * Extends acceptance-test-kit with helpers specific to the objective and
  5→ * behavior node feature set.
  6→ *
  7→ * All helpers use business language -- no technical jargon in function names.
  8→ *
  9→ * Driving ports:
 10→ *   POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/objectives       (objective CRUD)
 11→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/objectives        (list objectives)
 12→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/objectives/:id    (objective detail + progress)
 13→ *   POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behaviors         (behavior record creation)
